    "description": "To configure <tt>dnf-automatic</tt> to install only security updates\nautomatically, set <tt>upgrade_type</tt> to <tt>security</tt> under\n<tt>[commands]</tt> section in <tt>/etc/dnf/automatic.conf</tt>.",
